```

Get camera to train car mapping lookup table.

Response (20 cameras, 2 per car):
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "mappings": [
      { "cameraId": "car01_cam01", "zone": "car_1", "carId": 1 },
      { "cameraId": "car01_cam02", "zone": "car_1", "carId": 1 },
      { "cameraId": "car02_cam01", "zone": "car_2", "carId": 2 },
      { "cameraId": "car02_cam02", "zone": "car_2", "carId": 2 },
      ...
      { "cameraId": "car10_cam01", "zone": "car_10", "carId": 10 },
      { "cameraId": "car10_cam02", "zone": "car_10", "carId": 10 }
    ]
  }
}
```

Reset simulation to initial state.

Clears all train data, warnings, and decisions.
Broadcasts 'simulation_reset' event via WebSocket.

Response:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "message": "Simulation reset successfully",
    "timestamp": "2026-07-15T..."
  }
}
```

WebSocket endpoint for real-time updates.

Connect using WebSocket client (Postman WS tab, wscat, or browser).

Events received (all data is camelCase):

1. occupancy_updated
```json
{
  "type": "occupancy_updated",
  "trainId": "SF10-001",
  "timestamp": "2026-07-15T...",
  "data": {
    "car_id": 1,
    "person_count": 5,
    "occupancy_percentage": 2.5,
    "status": "LOW"
  }
}
```

2. prediction_updated
```json
{
  "type": "prediction_updated",
  "data": {
    "car_id": 1,
    "prediction": {
      "predicted_occupancy": 3.1,
      "risk_score": 0.1,
      "confidence": 0.7
    }
  }
}
```

3. recommendation_changed
```json
{
  "type": "recommendation_changed",
  "data": {
    "recommendation": {
      "action": "MOVE_PASSENGERS",
      "from_car_id": 4,
      "to_car_id": 1,
      "confidence": 0.85,
      "reason": "Car 4 is 92% full..."
    }
  }
}
```

4. warning_updated
```json
{
  "type": "warning_updated",
  "data": {
    "warning": {
      "train_id": "SF10-001",
      "car_id": 4,
      "warning_type": "HIGH_OCCUPANCY",
      "severity": "WARNING",
      "message": "Car 4 is HIGH (92.0%)",
      "is_active": true
    }
  }
}
```

5. camera_status_updated
```json
{
  "type": "camera_status_updated",
  "data": {
    "camera_id": "car01_cam01",
    "status": "active"
  }
}
```

6. system_health_updated
7. simulation_reset
